<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-39-0220 </DOCNO><TEXT>A systematic investigation of an orbifold inspired construction of supercurrentsfor string theories based on covariant lattices is presented. Using mathematicalresults on conjugacy classes of Weyl groups we classify the supercurrentsthat can be obtained, and discuss their properties. This also clarifiesthe intimate relation between rank 22 orbifolds and covariant lattices.</TEXT></DOC>